Rating: 4
Made this yesterday. Do follow instructions and prepare this at least a few hours before serving. Next time I make this I will use less oil. the quarter cup recommended left the ingredients swimming in oil. I also added a handful of toasted pine nuts. I would absolutely add them when I make this again - which will be soon. I was not diligent about the perfect strips of peppers when cutting - but the dish was still visually beautiful.

