Rating: 4
This was a taste explosion and absolutely amazing the next day. As a cheese lover, I added a few crumbles of goat feta as well, which worked quite nicely. My only caveat would be to other garlic lovers who might be tempted to add more than what's called for: I did, and thought it was too garlicky (very rare for me). Stick with the recipe!

